data.description: This beautiful home offers the perfect blend of country living and convenience. With three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, you'll have plenty of space for your family and guests. The house is situated on a sprawling 11-acre property, giving you ample room to explore and enjoy the great outdoors. Wildlife all over the property! New HVAC installed last year. All new flooring in dining room, kitchen and bedrooms installed last year. Huge laundry room!! Come check out the unique house and property!
